snippet.title: 7 Gates The Path To Zamolxes | Match 3 | FreeGamePick
snippet.description:
http://freegamepick.net/en/7-gates-the-path-to-zamolxes/
A long time ago, the Dacians asked their Gods to hide their treasures. You have been chosen to find the old treasures and return them to your people in 7 Gates: The Path to Zamolxes! 
Explore different temples and return home in this amazing game. Embrace your destiny as the chosen one as you progress through tons of levels and find the incredible treasure in 7 Gates: The Path to Zamolxes!
